import React from 'react'
import { View,Text,StyleSheet, ScrollView } from 'react-native'

export default function App() {
  return (
    <View style={{flex:1}}>
        <ScrollView>
    <View style={styles.HeadView}>
     
      <View style={styles.flexOneView}>
        <View style={{flex:0.6,backgroundColor:'#faba5a',borderRadius:10}}></View>
        <View style={{flex:0.3,backgroundColor:'#21c294',borderRadius:10}}></View>
      </View>
      <View style={styles.flexTwoView}>
        <View style={{flex:0.3,backgroundColor:'#2171c2',borderRadius:10}}></View>
        <View style={{flex:0.6,backgroundColor:'#db8f69',borderRadius:10}}></View>
      </View>
      <View style={styles.flexThreeView}>
      <View style={{flex:0.3,backgroundColor:'#c25c3a',borderRadius:10}}></View>
        <View style={{flex:0.3,backgroundColor:'#c79726',borderRadius:10}}></View>
        <View style={{flex:0.3,backgroundColor:'#2661c7',borderRadius:10}}></View>
      </View>
      <View style={styles.flexFourView}>
      <View style={{flex:0.3,backgroundColor:'#b07695',borderRadius:10}}></View>
        <View style={{flex:0.6,backgroundColor:'#47d6c1',borderRadius:10}}></View>
      </View>
      <View style={styles.flexFiveView}>
      <View style={{flex:0.3,backgroundColor:'#47d6c1',borderRadius:10}}></View>
        <View style={{flex:0.6,backgroundColor:'#c288a9',borderRadius:10}}></View>
      </View>
          
    </View>
    </ScrollView>
    </View>

  )
}
const styles=StyleSheet.create({
HeadView:{
    flex:1,
   top:20
},
flexOneView:{
   flex:1,
   flexDirection:'row',
   justifyContent:'space-evenly',
   margin:10
},
flexTwoView:{
    flexDirection:'row',
    flex:1,
    justifyContent:'space-evenly',
    margin:10
},
flexThreeView:{
    flexDirection:'row',
    flex:1,
    justifyContent:'space-evenly',
    margin:10
},
flexFourView:{
    flexDirection:'row',
    flex:1,
    justifyContent:'space-evenly',
    margin:10
},
flexFiveView:{
    flexDirection:'row',
    flex:1,
    justifyContent:'space-evenly',
    margin:10
}


})
